{
  "info": {
    "name": "Lead Management API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Real Estate Lead Management System (Feature 006)\n\n## Overview\n- Track potential clients through sales pipeline\n- Agent-level and manager-level access\n- Multi-tenancy with company isolation\n- Lead conversion to property sales\n\n## Authentication\nAll requests require:\n- `Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}` (OAuth 2.0)\n- `Cookie: session_id={{session_id}}` (Session)\n- `X-Company-ID: {{company_id}}` (Multi-tenancy)\n\n## Variables\nConfigure these in your Postman environment:\n- `base_url`: http://localhost:8069\n- `jwt_token`: OAuth token from authentication\n- `session_id`: Session ID from login\n- `company_id`: Company ID (1 for testing)\n- `lead_id`: Lead ID for detail operations\n- `property_id`: Property ID for conversions",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "lead-mgmt-006",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get OAuth Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('jwt_token', jsonData.access_token);",
                  "    console.log('JWT Token saved to environment');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"client_id\": \"{{client_id}}\",\n  \"client_secret\": \"{{client_secret}}\",\n  \"grant_type\": \"client_credentials\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/token",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "token"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "User Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('session_id', jsonData.data.session_id);",
                  "    console.log('Session ID saved to environment');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{username}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
